{
  "name": "AI HR Recruitment Assistant",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Recruitment Assistant\n**Trigger** -> New resume received via Webform or Email (gmail node)\n\n**Evaluate Resume** -> HR person goes through the resume and evaluates profile fitment.\n\n**Make Decision** -> HR person routes the profile based on the scoring and shortlisting of the profile \n\nScore > 7 -> Shortlist\n5-7 -> Add to \"maybe\" list\n< 5 -> Archive\n\n**Log and Track** -> HR person uploads the CV to cloud storage , makes an entry in the Job applicants tracker.\n\n**Notify** -> If shortlisted , HR person notifies the Hiring Manager and sends email to the candidate for short connet over phone.",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 624,
        "color": 5
      },
